{
  "stem": "10272.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't ask us, only the name, the year I was born, where I'm from, that's it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he didn't say where it was or nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know at that time where it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We saw it-- it's in Germany, because he speaks German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We saw when we passed the border between Hungary and Germany, it is in German.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All the streets-- street [INAUDIBLE] plates are written in German, right, on the-- on the roads.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we know we were in Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But exactly-- it was a name of a-- a name was there, but I don't remember exactly the name.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I registered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- we standing there and waiting outside again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was snowing terribly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they said, OK, let's go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He took us to a pla-- to a barn which is-- the barn was outside of the camp actually, not inside of the camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then they took again this barn around with-- with wire, with-- with a-- with a fence so we couldn't go away.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They fenced us in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They made us to work and-- and-- and make for ourselves bunk beds.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They build us all kind of this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we ourselves, we got nails and hammers and we started to work and do this bunk beds.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And each one get a blanket, and also a dish-- a metal dish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We should go and get-- [INAUDIBLE] they would bring to us this big pot, and they would give us soup to eat.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And tomorrow morning, we going to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So next morning, they took us to work in a-- in a-- out of this-- in the village, there was a wooden area.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There was wood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wooden area.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were-- we were-- we were cutting the wood, this-- the trees.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to carry these trees from the hills down to the road, where a truck would come and pick it up.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was-- lasted a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they put us to work in the trenches, to dig with a shovel, deep in the trenches.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was in such a way that the tank would come down in an angle, right?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from the other side, he couldn't-- he couldn't come out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He would get stuck in these trenches.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A deep trench, but with a-- with a triangle, like a triangle way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was-- it was done in the whole-- the whole area, the whole area, miles, and miles, and miles.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were working on that-- on that job.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were happy to do it, because it was so cold.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not dressed, and this way we got warmed up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we didn't feel the frost and the-- and the-- the cold so much.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the morning, we got soup, the-- also the same thing, coffee or a tea and a slice of bread.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For lunch we got a soup with a slice of bread and a piece of margarine-- a small piece.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For dinner, we got-- we got again a soup, a slice of bread, and a piece of salami.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we had some kind of a-- we figured how many calories it is, approximately the sa-- the calorie we could make it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were still young so we-- we could overcome this hard work and survive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But then, one day, I fell when I was working.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "During the work I had some-- some problem.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I felt pain in my-- under my belly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was that I hadn't had-- it was-- I felt it was a hernia or something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It bothered me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I told my pals about it, what to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they said, don't do it, because those-- he spoke to some-- the guy who went to-- to get the-- the-- the pot with-- with soup from the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He had to go-- he is the only one who has contact with other-- with other prisoners.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So from them we find out that this is a military prisoner of war camp in which the prisoners are either Russians, French, or British.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "A few British too, but they're mostly French.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said, when he-- when he was asking, where are we now?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said we are satellite stalag-- satellite stalag camp of prisoners, which we get all the provisions from Mauthausen, not far from here.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if something is-- happens, they took us there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we know that we are not far from-- from Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the next cities in the-- in the area were called Fellbach and there was Linz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Linz is one city, and Fellbach.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Between Linz and Fellbach is located the concentration camp, Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were one of the satellites working for this proj-- job.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this we knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
